### 2.2 SwarnaVyapar

**Website:** https://swarnavyapar.in  
**HQ:** Zaveri Bazaar, Mumbai, Maharashtra  
**Tagline:** "#1 AI-Powered Jewellery Management Software in India"  
**Users:** 500+ jewellers across India (self-reported)  
**Deployment:** Cloud SaaS (web + mobile)  

#### Product Vision
A modern, design-forward, AI-native jewellery management application for retail showroom owners. Differentiated by AI voice commands and invoice scanning. Positioned as the "modern alternative" to legacy windows-based ERP solutions like Jwelly.

#### Target Segments
| Segment | Focus |
|---|---|
| Retail Showroom Owner | Billing, inventory, CRM, AI assistant |
| Showroom Manager | Voice-driven operations, analytics |
| Sales Counter Staff | Fast billing, stock lookup |

> ⚠️ **No dedicated B2B / Wholesale / Dealer module.** SwarnaVyapar is exclusively a B2C retail tool.

#### Full Feature Breakdown

**AI SUITE (Core Identity)**
- **AI Voice Assistant:** Create invoices, fetch stock, query analytics via voice commands. Marketed as "saves 3x time"
- **Swarna AI Business Analyst:** Ask business questions in plain English — "show me low stock items", "who are my top customers this month", "what sold most this Diwali" — gets instant structured answers
- **AI Invoice Digitization (Vendor Invoice Scanning):** Point phone camera at any vendor paper invoice; AI extracts line items, weights, and rates (claims 92% accuracy). Supports Hindi, English, regional scripts
- **Demand Forecasting:** AI predicts seasonal demand spikes (case study: 90% accuracy on Akshaya Tritiya demand prediction)

**BILLING & INVOICING**
- GST-compliant invoice creation
- Live gold rate integration (rates auto-update in pricing)
- Making charges integration
- Mobile-shareable customer invoice outputs
- Built for high counter-speed during peak showroom hours

**INVENTORY MANAGEMENT**
- QR-tagged inventory (auto-generates QR codes: G001, G002...)
- Bulk import (claims: "Add 100 items in 5 minutes")
- Mobile camera barcode/QR scanning (iPhone or Android)
- Smart low-stock alerts
- Audit trail — every change logged with timestamp
- Claims: 70% faster audits vs. manual; 100% accuracy; 2-second scan speed
- 50K+ items tracked across all customers (platform metric)
- Fast-moving inventory visibility, low-stock risk dashboard
- Category health tracking

**ONLINE DIGITAL CATALOGUE**
- Transforms inventory into an online visual catalogue
- One-tap WhatsApp sharing with customers
- Smart search within catalogue
- Customer wishlist / save favourites
- Auto-updated pricing (linked to live gold rates)

**FINANCIAL MANAGEMENT**
- Digital Khata Book (replaces paper ledgers)
- WhatsApp payment reminders (one-tap to send)
- Gold loan / Girvi tracking with auto-interest calculation
- Loan due date tracking and agreement printing
- Audit trail on all transactions
- Available 24/7 with bank-grade security

**CRM & LOYALTY**
- Automated rewards points system
- Tiered rewards: Gold, Platinum, Diamond tiers (auto-upgrade)
- Points calculated automatically per purchase (gold, silver, diamond)
- Redeem points directly on invoice
- Customer lifetime value (LTV) tracking
- Purchase pattern analysis per customer
- Claims: 40% increase in repeat sales; 3x retention

**PLATFORM CAPABILITIES**
- Offline operation with auto-sync when online
- Military-grade encryption (self-reported)
- Multi-user support with granular permission roles (owner/manager/staff)
- Works on web; mobile app available

**PRICING MODEL**
- 3-tier SaaS model:
  - **Starter** — Essential tools for individual jewellers
  - **Professional** — Advanced management for growing stores
  - **Business** — Enterprise solution for established chains
- Specific prices not listed; "No credit card required. Upgrade anytime."

**GAPS / WEAKNESSES**
- No B2B / wholesale / dealer management capability at all
- No order punching / approval workflow
- No multi-owner isolation (not designed for a single owner with 100+ dealers)
- Very new company — limited track record
- No dynamic custom field schema
- No AI visual similarity search for product discovery
- No auto-tagging from product images on upload
- WhatsApp sharing is one-directional (push), not a two-way dealer ordering portal
- No detailed analytics on dealer behaviour / inactive dealers / dealer leaderboard
- Wishlist is for customer B2C use, not B2B dealer use

