### 2.3 JewelMaker

**Website:** https://jewelmaker.ai  
**HQ:** Ahmedabad, Gujarat (Times Square, Thaltej)  
**Tagline:** "Simplify all jewellery operations in just 7 days"  
**Users:** 110+ Indian jewellers (self-reported)  
**Deployment:** Cloud SaaS + Offline capability  

#### Product Vision
An operationally practical, rapidly deployable all-in-one tool for every segment of the jewellery supply chain — with a strong focus on the Indian market's multi-lingual, multi-channel needs. Marketing emphasizes rapid onboarding ("live in 1 day, trained in 7 days").

#### Target Segments
| Segment | Focus |
|---|---|
| Retailer | POS, Tablet Catalog, CRM, GST Billing |
| Wholesaler | Bulk orders, B2B Customer Portal, Catalogue |
| Manufacturer | Production, Karigar, Cost Calculation |

#### Full Feature Breakdown

**FOR RETAILERS**
- Quick GST-compliant invoicing (claims: billing in 2-3 minutes)
- Multiple payment mode support
- Automatic tax calculation
- Real-time stock updates with easy stock transfers
- RFID integration (for premium showrooms)
- Barcode scanning and generation
- Customizable price tags
- Customer Profile Management (purchase history, preferences, custom orders)
- Monthly Scheme Programs (chit fund / savings scheme integration)
- Karigar work tracking
- Multi-store management from central dashboard
- Sales analytics and reporting
- Tablet-based product catalog (for over-the-counter browsing with customer)
- Offline capability at exhibitions with auto-sync on reconnect

**FOR WHOLESALERS**
- **B2B Customer Portal:** *Self-service ordering for retailers* — this is the most relevant competitive feature
- Bulk order management and handling
- Bulk Sales / Purchase workflows
- Live order tracking for both parties
- GST billing for B2B transactions
- Customized pricing for different B2B customers
- Credit limit management per customer
- Inventory forecasting
- Hours & Minutes-based product allocation
- Automated push notifications on order status
- Digital catalog creation and sharing
- Real-time product updates in catalog
- WhatsApp integration for catalog sharing
- Profitability analysis per customer

**FOR MANUFACTURERS**
- Real-time production tracking across workstations
- Precise gold and gemstone inventory tracking
- Wastage calculation per production stage
- Material allocation per order
- Karigar performance monitoring
- Quality control checkpoints
- Accurate cost calculation per piece
- Labor cost tracking
- Digital design catalog creation from manufacturing stage
- Work-in-progress monitoring
- Production capacity planning
- Integration with CAD/CAM design software (claimed)

**PLATFORM-WIDE**
- Offline/online with automatic syncing
- Data stored in India (data residency compliance)
- Bank-level security (claimed)
- Role-based access (owner, manager, staff)
- 24/7 support in Hindi, Gujarati, Marathi, English
- Free setup and training (onboarding in 1 day)
- Regular technical updates

**PRICING**
- No public pricing; contact/demo model
- Referral program in place (suggests freemium or partner-driven growth)

**GAPS / WEAKNESSES**
- B2B Customer Portal is mentioned but appears shallow — no evidence of:
  - Cart persistence across sessions
  - Order approval workflow (Pending → Approved → Rejected / Partial Approval)
  - Line-item level partial approval
  - Automated inventory deduction on approval
  - Real-time catalogue with WebSocket updates
- No AI features whatsoever (no AI tagging, no visual similarity search, no NLP search, no demand forecasting, no business digest)
- No dynamic custom fields schema
- No dealer-specific analytics (leaderboard, inactive dealers alert, preference analysis)
- No visual similarity search (consumer-grade discovery)
- No wishlist for B2B dealers
- No product collection/campaign grouping feature

